**My Interactive Personal Portfolio âœ¨**

This is a fully responsive, single-page personal portfolio website built with HTML, Tailwind CSS, and vanilla JavaScript. It's designed to be easily customizable and deployable on services like GitHub Pages, showcasing your skills and projects in a sleek, modern way.

**ðŸš€ Features**

AI-Powered Content Generation: Use the Gemini API to automatically generate professional bio suggestions and enhance your project descriptions, saving you time and boosting your content's impact.

Complete Customization Panel: Instantly switch between Dark/Light Mode, choose from multiple color themes, or pick a custom color with the color wheel. You can even change the hero background.

Dynamic Content Management: Add, edit, and delete all portfolio sections (Skills, Projects, etc.) directly on the page without reloading.

Ready for Action: Includes a functional "Download CV" button and a front-end "Send Message" contact form.

Structured for easy deployment: Built with a clean architecture that makes it ready to go live on GitHub Pages with just a few clicks.

